metrics_conclusion: Can't Buy Me Love has higher complexity than the average song  in terms Chord Complexity and Chord Progression Novelty.
key_conclusion: Can't Buy Me Love has sections analyzed in the following keys: C Dorian,  and C Major.  Click on the linked cheat sheets for popular chords, chord progressions, downloadable midi files and more!

metadata.editComments: Converted to parallel dorian, since all chords jump between mixolydian, major and dorian but melody is always in dorian, I think it makes more sense to label it as dorian overall
